{"type": "article", "id": 24824, "title": "带有阴影的极简卫浴系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153215ipH1RlZfo9vU7Im2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 为意大利品牌 Ex.t 设计的极简卫浴系列，包括洗手池、澡盆和、镜子和磨砂玻璃灯。第一眼看上去它们都在最基本的几何图形中，不同的是洗手池和澡盆的边缘增加了半圈弧形隔板，可以置物，也让几何图形显得很微妙。而镜子和磨砂玻璃灯的外圈也多了一层半透明的玻璃，有一种阴影的效果，突出了它的层次。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153212BFoX1eZCfuj3dzQY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153212xDXEwkc6zYNmSdF7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153213WDjRet8QpuoTix3L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75213675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153213uERjPs9WKUkB2JVq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33440171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153214gPsZmKhpA4dYXNDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33440171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}